l details decorate the background, giving the toy section a playful fantasy setting. He holds the long yellow blaster tube across his body, then lifts it upright. A large blue jagged starburst appears on the right with white text, “LAYAWAY TODAY.” The shelves and floor are crowded with purple-and-black Ghostbusters packaging, making the store look full of available toys.\n\nThe scene fades into a green background with the red-and-white Hills logo centered near the bottom. A small square badge beside it reads “LOW PRICE PROMISE.” The final view holds on the green background with the Hills logo and the low-price badge, while partial white lettering begins to appear at the left.",
